avdta.network.node.policy

Class SignalWeightedTBR

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.network.node.IntersectionControl
      • avdta.network.node.TBR
        • avdta.network.node.PriorityTBR
          • avdta.network.node.policy.SignalWeightedTBR
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DelayWeights, Signalized

    public class SignalWeightedTBR
extends PriorityTBR
implements Signalized, DelayWeights
    This class implements a signal-weighted reservations. Vehicle waiting time is weighted by how much capacity the traffic signal allocates to their turning movement. The SignalWeightedTBR is a Signalized; it does not implement a traffic signal, but uses the signal timing data.
